| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5028 — Recovery Inhibition (threeam)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 79aa9313-e6aa-54f5-8890-c9c7eaa9b0c1"
